title: Jerry Maguire [1996] OST
description:
Jerry Macguire Soundtrack.  Like most soundtracks some of the songs we loved in the movie are left out. But hey that goes with the territory, enjoy :)

1. Magic Bus - Townshend, Pete  
2. Sitting Still Moving Still Staring Outlooking - Defever, Warren  
3. Getting in Tune - Townshend, Pete  
4. Pocketful of Rainbows - Wise, Fred  
5. World on a String - Young, Neil  
6. We Meet Again - Wilson, Nancy [2]  
7. The Horses - Jones, Rickie Lee  
8. Secret Garden - Springsteen, Bruce  
9. Singalong Junk - McCartney, Paul  
10. Wise Up - Mann, Aimee  
11. Momma Miss America - McCartney, Paul  
12. Sandy - Wilson, Nancy [2]  
13. Shelter from the Storm - Dylan, Bob
